{
  "title": "05 — VLM Worker",
  "uid": "kathir-05-vlm-worker",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "tags": [
    "kathir",
    "platform"
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 5
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 05 — VLM Worker\nThe clip-reasoning VLM plugin host (VLMClipReasoningPlugin). TTFT (`model_ttft_ms`) and decode tok/s (`model_tokens_per_second`) gate latency; `model_json_parse_total` tracks structured-output health (aim ~100% ok); `model_verdict_total` shows the verdict distribution. The VLM only runs on suspicious windows (cascade gating, spec/11). Metrics: `model_*` filtered `task=\"suspicious_event_verification\"`."
      },
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "VLM requests",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "marlin-metrics"
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "purple"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(model_requests_total{task=\"suspicious_event_verification\"})",
          "legendFormat": "VLM requests"
        }
      ],
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Output tokens",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "marlin-metrics"
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
